title: Identify the Structure
text: Think about a structure that organizes data in a grid format, similar to a spreadsheet.

title: Consider Common Data Structures
text: Consider common data structures used in programming and data analysis, such as arrays, lists, and tables.

title: Focus on Rows and Columns
text: Data organized in both rows and columns are two-dimensional.

title: Dimension
text: Arrays and Lists are both one-dimensional.
